@startuml
title 미핏 - 티켓 라이프사이클 시퀀스 (Grant / Use / Refund / Expire + 일일 리셋)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ActorBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #2196F3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantFontSize 11
  BoxBorderColor #B0BEC5
  BoxBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
}

actor "사용자" as U
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend\n(SignUp /\nStartInterview /\nGenerateReport)" as BE
participant "BaseTicketService\n(공통 상위)" as BTS
database "PostgreSQL\n(UserTicket\n+ TicketLog\n+ select_for_update)" as DB
queue "Redis\n(broker)" as Q
participant "Celery Beat\n(스케줄러)" as Beat
participant "Celery Worker\n(GrantDailySubscription\nTicketsTask)" as W

== Step 1. 회원가입 시 초기 티켓 발급 (FR-SUB-03) ==

U -> FE : 회원가입
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/users/sign-up/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : SignUpService.execute()
  BE -> BE : GrantInitialSubscriptionTicketsService(user).perform()
  BE -> DB : Subscription 조회 (FREE 플랜)
  BE -> DB : SubscriptionPlanTicketPolicy\n.objects.get(plan_type=FREE)\n→ daily_ticket_amount
  BE -> DB : UserTicket.objects.update_or_create(\n  user=user,\n  defaults={ daily_count: N, purchased_count: 0 }\n)
  note right of DB : 초기 발급은 TicketLog 미생성\n(정책적 결정)
  BE --> FE : 200 OK + JWT
deactivate BE

== Step 2. 면접 시작 시 차감 (FR-TICKET-02) ==

U -> FE : "면접 시작"
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/interviews/interview-sessions/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : StartInterviewView.post()
  BE -> BTS : UseTicketsService(user, amount=ticket_cost,\n  reason=f"{session_type} 면접 시작").perform()
  activate BTS
    BTS -> DB : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE\nUserTicket (user)
    note right of DB
      _get_or_create_ticket_with_lock()
      → row-level lock 획득
      (FR-TICKET-06 동시성 제어)
    end note
    BTS -> BTS : ticket.deduct(amount)\n(daily_count 우선, 부족하면 purchased_count)
    BTS -> DB : UserTicket.save() + TicketLog 저장\n(action=USE, amount=-N, balance_after=...,\n  reason="...")
  deactivate BTS
  BE -> DB : InterviewSession 생성 + 첫 질문 LLM 호출
  BE --> FE : { uuid, first_question }
deactivate BE

== Step 3. 분석 리포트 생성 시 차감 (FR-TICKET-02) ==

U -> FE : "분석 리포트 생성"
FE -> BE : POST /api/v1/interviews/{uuid}/generate-report/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : GenerateAnalysisReportView.post()
  BE -> BTS : UseTicketsService(user, amount=TICKET_COST_ANALYSIS_REPORT,\n  reason="면접 분석 리포트 생성").perform()
  activate BTS
    BTS -> DB : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE UserTicket
    BTS -> DB : UserTicket.save() + TicketLog(USE)
  deactivate BTS
  BE -> Q : dispatch generate_analysis_report task
  BE --> FE : 202 Accepted
deactivate BE

== Step 4. 일일 티켓 리셋 (Celery Beat — KST 00:00) ==

Beat -> Q : crontab(hour=0, minute=0)\n→ GrantDailySubscriptionTicketsTask
Q -> W : pull task
activate W
  W -> W : GrantDailySubscriptionTicketsService.execute()
  W -> DB : SubscriptionPlanTicketPolicy\n  .objects.filter(is_active=True)
  loop policy in policies
    W -> DB : Subscription.objects.filter(\n  plan_type=policy.plan_type, status=ACTIVE)
    loop sub in subscriptions
      W -> DB : UserTicket.objects.update_or_create(\n  user=sub.user,\n  defaults={ daily_count: policy.daily_ticket_amount }\n)
      note right of DB : 일일 리셋 — TicketLog 미생성\n(누적 카운트 아님, 정책상 덮어쓰기)
    end
  end
deactivate W

== Step 5. 티켓 환불 (FR-TICKET-03 — 정의됨, 호출 사이트 미구현) ==

note over BE, BTS
  RefundTicketsService 정의 완료:
    - target=PURCHASED 기본
    - TicketLog(action=REFUND, amount=+N) 기록
  현재 호출 사이트 없음 (To-Be):
    - 면접 의도적 취소 시
    - 분석 리포트 실패 시
end note

opt (To-Be) 면접 취소 환불
  U -> FE : "면접 취소"
  FE -> BE : POST /interview-sessions/{uuid}/cancel/
  BE -> BTS : RefundTicketsService(user, amount=ticket_cost).perform()
  BTS -> DB : SELECT FOR UPDATE + ticket.add() + TicketLog(REFUND)
end

== Step 6. 티켓 만료 (To-Be — 서비스만 정의됨) ==

note over Beat, W
  ExpireTicketsService 정의 완료:
    - 시한부 프로모션 티켓 만료 처리
    - TicketLog(action=EXPIRE, amount=-N)
  ExpireTicketsTask (BaseScheduledTask) 미구현
  → 향후 Celery Beat 스케줄로 등록 예정
end note

footer MeFit - 티켓 라이프사이클 (FR-SUB-01~03 + FR-TICKET-01~06)
@enduml
